Hi Bart,
You can get them for less than $3.00 (-at-)
_http://www.bus-boys.com/aircoolsystem71.html_ 
(http://www.bus-boys.com/aircoolsystem71.html) 
You really do not want to use a tighter spring like the carb cable return  
spring.  That could interfere with the flaps from closing all the  way.  It just 
needs to be strong enough so that if the linkage fails the  flaps will open.
Eric&Barb
